    + Add App Grid.
    + Add Ubuntu Software Center.
    + Add Hardinfo.
    + Add Disks.
    + Add SpiderOakONE.
    + Add Chromium as an alternative to Google Chrome.
    + Add categories to Software.
    + Add proprietary software toggle.
