    + Assorted content updates and whitespace cleanup.
    + Update content for Introduction and Features, assorted content
    changes and whitespace cleanup throughout.
    + Update buttons in Software to make them consistent.
    + Rename to Welcome.
    + Hide some elements when in a live session.
